msgstr "量詞"

#: ../../T/two-to-the-N.rst:9
msgid ""
"An amount much larger than :ref:`N` but smaller than :ref:`infinity`\\. \"I "
"have 2-to-the-``N`` things to do before I can go out for lunch\" means you "
"probably won't show up."
msgstr ""
"\\ :ref:`N`\\ よりはるかに大きいが\\ :ref:`infinity`\\ より小さい量。「昼食に出かける前に2-to-the-\\ "
"``N``\\ 個のすべきことがある」は、おそらく現れないだろうという意味。"
